<plot>In this Flemish comical format, adapted from a popular radio show also on public broadcaster VRT, presenter Jo Van Damme and an alternating panel make fun of celebrities, each-other and anyone they can drag into it, including brave audience members who volunteer to take the microphone for a question, in various ways that change over the seasons, such as commenting on articles and photos in the press, TV programs, showbiz, Flemish and foreign news etc.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?132209</url></doc>
